    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/Header.tsx`, which implements the responsive navigation bar. It features the signature GoldenCare logo, custom typography, links to service categories (\"Assisted Living\", \"Memory Care\", \"Independent Living\"), and a CTA button that acts as the entry point for interactive searches. It includes a mobile-friendly hamburger drawer."
