    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/AdvisorChat.tsx` to build the interactive slide-over chat interface representing our AI Care Concierge, \"Sarah\". It integrates with our backend Express `/api/chat` endpoint and comes pre-loaded with sample starter questions, a professional typing animation, and responsive bubble styles matching GoldenCare\'s design identity."
