    thinking: "**Verifying System Integrity**\n\nI\'m pleased to report the dev server restart was successful! Now, I\'m quickly confirming the linter and compiler remain \"green\" \342\200\223 a standard check, as it shouldn\'t cause issues, but always good practice to ensure everything\'s ship-shape after a restart.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have successfully built and deployed **GoldenCare**, a highly polished, full-stack senior care search platform and interactive AI concierge. Here is a summary of the implemented architecture, visual layout, and features:\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual & Design System\n- **Sage and Cream Palette**: Framed the experience using a soft off-white/cream canvas (`#FAF6EE`), layered with organic accent blobs in light sage green (`#E3ECE1`) and warm terracotta-beige (`#E7DFD4`).\n- **Aesthetic Typography Pairing**: Paired \"Lora\" (a premium, editorial serif) for prominent display headings with \"Inter\" (a highly legible, versatile sans-serif) for body copies and technical details, matching the provided mockup screens precisely.\n- **Asymmetric Image Masks**: Structured the core visual assets (such as the senior gardening couple) using asymmetric, fluid border-radius frames to recreate the organic, friendly visual flow of the design files.\n\n### \342\232\231\357\270\217 Core Technical Modules\n1. **Full-Stack Express + Vite Server**: Set up a robust, unified full-stack architecture. Vite compiles static assets seamlessly, while an Express backend handles custom REST endpoints, keeping environmental keys hidden from the browser.\n2. **AI Senior Care Concierge (`/api/chat`)**: Built a secure chat endpoint that leverages the Google GenAI SDK (`gemini-3.5-flash`). Sarah\342\200\224our AI Advisor\342\200\224supports families with empathetic, structural advice on Assisted Living, Memory Care, and Independent Living. If the Gemini API key is unconfigured or missing, the server uses a compassionate rule-based fallback system to guarantee uptime.\n3. **Interactive Partner Directories**: Implemented a comprehensive search page loaded with high-quality, pre-vetted senior living communities in San Francisco and Oakland. Users can filter listings by care categories, cities, text keywords, and pricing sliders.\n4. **Tour Booking & Scheduler**: Developed an integrated reservation system. Families can select dates, choose specific hours, and book site tours. Successful schedules display direct coordinates and transition checklists.\n5. **Durable Local Storage Engine**: Integrated client-side state persistence. Any booked tours are tracked locally, allowing families to manage, view, or cancel scheduled visits through a responsive floating dashboard."
    thinking_duration {
      nanos: 557817104
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
